' =============================================================================
' GTNH Platform — User Flow: Ore Processing Chain & Voltage Tiers
' 2 диаграммы: ore processing chain, voltage tiers & transformers
' =============================================================================

' ===========================================================================
' 1. Ore processing chain (classic GTNH doubling)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml orep-chain
title **Flow O1: Ore Processing Chain (руда -> пластина)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "Macerator" as Mac
participant "Furnace" as Furn
participant "Compressor" as Comp
participant "RecipeManager" as RM
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "ItemPipe" as IP

== Фаза 1: Дробление (Macerator) ==

Tick -> Mac: tick(dt)
Mac -> RM: FindRecipe(macerator_id, input=[ore_iron])
RM --> Mac: Recipe found: crushed_iron x2
Mac -> PN: CheckEnergy(macerator_id, cost_per_tick)
PN --> Mac: Energy OK

Mac -> Mac: Advance progress (20 Hz)
alt Recipe complete
    Mac -> Mac: Consume 1 ore_iron
    Mac -> Mac: Output 2 crushed_iron
    Mac -> IP: Push crushed_iron to output pipe
end

== Фаза 2: Плавка (Furnace) ==

IP -> Furn: Deliver crushed_iron to input

Tick -> Furn: tick(dt)
Furn -> RM: FindRecipe(furnace_id, input=[crushed_iron])
RM --> Furn: Recipe found: iron_ingot x1
Furn -> PN: CheckEnergy(furnace_id, cost_per_tick)
PN --> Furn: Energy OK

Furn -> Furn: Advance progress
alt Recipe complete
    Furn -> Furn: Consume 2 crushed_iron
    Furn -> Furn: Output 1 iron_ingot
    Furn -> IP: Push iron_ingot to output pipe
end

== Фаза 3: Сжатие (Compressor) ==

IP -> Comp: Deliver iron_ingot to input

Tick -> Comp: tick(dt)
Comp -> RM: FindRecipe(compressor_id, input=[iron_ingot])
RM --> Comp: Recipe found: iron_plate x1
Comp -> PN: CheckEnergy(compressor_id, cost_per_tick)
PN --> Comp: Energy OK

Comp -> Comp: Advance progress
alt Recipe complete
    Comp -> Comp: Consume 1 iron_ingot
    Comp -> Comp: Output 1 iron_plate
end

== Итог: 1 руда -> 2 пластины ==

note right #E67E22
  Classic GTNH doubling:
  1 ore_iron
    -> Macerator: 2 crushed_iron
      -> Furnace: 2 iron_ingots
        -> Compressor: 2 iron_plates

  Требует: 3 машины + item pipes + energy
  Всё работает без игрока
end note

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 2. Voltage tiers & transformers
' ===========================================================================
@startuml orep-voltage-tiers
title **Flow O2: Voltage Tiers & Transformers**

actor "Player / System" as Actor
participant "Machine\n(EnergyStorage)" as Machine
participant "Cable" as Cable
participant "Transformer" as XFMR
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "GameClient" as Client

== GregTech voltage tiers ==

note right #438D80
  GTNH Voltage Tiers:
  ULV (0) =    8 EU/t
  LV  (1) =   32 EU/t
  MV  (2) =  128 EU/t
  HV  (3) =  512 EU/t
  EV  (4) = 2048 EU/t
  IV  (5) = 8192 EU/t
  LuV (6) = 32768 EU/t
  ZPM (7) = 131072 EU/t
  UV  (8) = 524288 EU/t
  UHV (9) = 2097152 EU/t
end note

== Machine tier vs Cable tier ==

Actor -> Machine: Устанавливает машину (MV tier)

Machine -> Cable: Connect to energy network
Cable --> Machine: Cable tier = LV / MV / HV

alt Cable tier >= Machine tier (MV >= MV)
    Machine -> PN: RequestEnergy
    PN --> Machine: Energy delivered OK
    Machine -> Machine: Normal operation

else Cable tier < Machine tier (LV < MV)
    note right #E74C3C
      Cable перегружен!
      Cable maxVoltage < Machine потребление
    end
    PN -> PN: Cable overheat
    PN -> PN: Cable destroyed (explosion)
    PN -> Client: Broadcast explosion event
    Client -> Client: Show explosion effect

else Machine tier < Source tier (MV machine, HV source)
    note right #E74C3C
      Машина получит слишком
      много EU/t -> взрыв!
    end
    Machine -> Machine: Overvoltage
    Machine -> Machine: Machine destroyed
end

== Transformer: решение проблемы ==

Actor -> Machine: Ставит Transformer между source и machine

note right #5899DA
  Transformer:
  - Step Down: HV(512) -> MV(128)
  - 1 face = high voltage side
  - 5 faces = low voltage side
  - Machine получает MV -> OK
end note

Machine -> XFMR: Connected via MV side
PN -> XFMR: Input: HV (512 EU/t)
XFMR -> XFMR: Step down: 512 -> 128 EU/t
XFMR -> Machine: Output: MV (128 EU/t)
Machine -> Machine: Normal operation

== Machine GUI: tier info ==

Client -> Client: MachineWindow shows:
note right
  - Current tier (e.g. MV)
  - Energy input EU/t
  - MaxInput / MaxOutput
  - Overvoltage warning if mismatch
end note

@enduml
